data.description: Welcome to a truly exceptional hilltop estate, offering the epitome of luxury living with unrivaled Hill Country and Downtown City views. This remarkable property boasts 5 bedrooms, 4.5 baths, and an opulent Primary Suite featuring a beautifully renovated en suite bath that defines indulgence. Step outside to discover an in-ground lap pool with an entrancing negative edge, providing an oasis of tranquility. The kitchen is a chef's dream with a wet bar right around the corner. For car enthusiasts, the estate presents a 6-car garage haven, comprising a 3-car attached garage and a separate 3-car detached open-air garage that delivers panoramic vistas - an automotive paradise with a view. Additionally, a charming one-bedroom guest house complete with a full kitchen and a balcony provides the perfect retreat for guests. Every room in this exquisite residence opens to balconies or patios, inviting you to savor the breathtaking views at every turn. Whether you're observing the wonders of nature or the spectacle of fireworks over Fiesta Texas, this one-of-a-kind, all-inclusive 2.18-acre estate offers a lifestyle of exclusivity and convenience. Located just 5 minutes from IH-10 and the 1604 Corridor, and within 10 minutes of La Cantera, Valero, USAA, The Rim, UTSA, and Fiesta Texas, this is the pinnacle of Hill Country luxury living. Don't miss your chance to own this extraordinary property.
